{{!
    @template format_smartcards/local/cm_icon

    Decorative content of one card's icon circle: the teacher's custom emoji or bundled
    library icon when configured (SmartCards appearance, type=emoji or type=icon),
    otherwise the default per-module-type icon. Always aria-hidden — the real accessible
    name is the card's text title, rendered by the caller.

    A bundled library icon (isbsicon) renders as a CSS-masked span instead of a plain
    img: its bundled SVG uses fill="currentColor", which an isolated <img> document can
    never inherit from the page, so recolouring it needs mask-image + background-color
    on the wrapper instead (see appearance_style_resolver::resolve()). An uploaded image
    or the default per-module-type icon is a real, already-coloured picture, so it
    always stays a plain img.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "isemoji": false,
        "emoji": "",
        "iscustomicon": true,
        "customiconurl": "#",
        "iconurl": "#",
        "isbsicon": true,
        "hasiconcolorstyle": true,
        "iconcolorstyle": "background-color: #1565c0"
    }
}}
{{#isemoji}}
<span class="sc-card-emoji">{{emoji}}</span>
{{/isemoji}}
{{^isemoji}}
    {{#iscustomicon}}
        {{#isbsicon}}
        <span
            class="sc-card-iconimg sc-card-iconimg--masked"
            style="-webkit-mask-image: url({{customiconurl}}); mask-image: url({{customiconurl}}){{#hasiconcolorstyle}}; {{iconcolorstyle}}{{/hasiconcolorstyle}}"
        ></span>
        {{/isbsicon}}
        {{^isbsicon}}
        <img src="{{customiconurl}}" alt="" class="sc-card-iconimg">
        {{/isbsicon}}
    {{/iscustomicon}}
    {{^iscustomicon}}
    <img src="{{iconurl}}" alt="" class="sc-card-iconimg">
    {{/iscustomicon}}
{{/isemoji}}
